Subject: [PATCH 0033/1072] ARM: dts: imx6q{dl}: add DTE pads for uart

git://git.freescale.com/imx/linux-2.6-imx.git imx_3.10.17_1.0.0_beta
commit 03e1732c34f2f0da5963b29d57166ac68ee81c9c

The uart2 in the imx6q-arm2 board is used as a DTE uart,
this patch adds the necessary DTE pads for uart2.

Signed-off-by: Huang Shijie <b32955@freescale.com>
